      "acceptanceCriteria": "Not required at MRL 2 when operating envelope overlap is demonstrated under Relevance of validation activities factor.",
      "rationale": "Equivalency of input parameters between validation and COU is addressed through the Relevance of validation activities factor. No separate assessment required at MRL 2."
    }
  ],
