    "actor": "https://uofa.net/synth/actor/morrison-credibility-team",
    "role": "Credibility assessment team",
    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "All seven assessed credibility factors meet or exceed their required gradation levels at MRL 2. Six factors are appropriately scoped to Gradation 1 and not assessed per MRL 2 guidance. The CFD model demonstrates sufficient credibility to support identification of worst-case hemolysis operating conditions for the Class II CPB device. The relative hemolysis index criterion (RH < 1) is met across all five evaluated operating points. The assessment team accepts the model for the stated COU.",
